title_name: High Level Krill Oil | Ultra Premium Pure North Pacific Ocean Krill Oil with Omega-3, EPA, DHA - 30 Soft Gels - 500mg
feature_bullets: ENHANCED BIO-AVAILABILITY: Omega-3 fatty acids in Krill oil attach to phospholipids as opposed to triglycerides, which in simple terms makes the omega-3 easier to absorb. As such, a lower dose of Krill is required to gain the same benefit as a higher dose of standard fish oil.,ULTRA PURE: While many fish oils contain detectable levels of toxins like mercury, krill oil does not. This is due to the position of krill in the marine food chain as these tiny creatures feed only on phytoplankton which do not contain mercury. In fact, omega-3 sourced from krill is considered to be the purest on the planet.,INCREASE CARDIOVASCULAR & JOINT HEALTH: Joints and bones not feeling as healthy and strong as they used to? Joint problems are often caused by inflammation. Rich doses of Omega-3 have shown to reduce joint stiffness and increase flexibility. Don't let age or injury keep you down!,SUPERCHARGE BRAIN HEALTH & MEMORY: With its high concentration of Omega-3’s, Krill oil is a superior source of docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and promotes improved brain health, including much-needed support for your memory.,BOOST MOOD: Studies have linked both EPA and DHA with anti-depressive effects and mood enhancement. Again, this is the result of Omega-3 leading to an increase in healthy hormone levels, which along with a boost in dopamine and serotonin can have a dramatic effect on mood and can help combat depression.

title_name: NativePath Antarctic Krill Oil - Wild-Caught Omega 3 Krill Oil 500mg Softgels with EPA, DHA and Astaxanthin - Omega 3 Supplement for Joint, Heart, Brain and Immunity - 60 ct - No Fishy Aftertaste
feature_bullets: Wild-Caught Omega 3 Supplement: Our wild-caught omega-3 krill oil is extracted from Antarctica's pristine waters. Having virtually no exposure to oceanic substances makes Antarctica a pure source of omega-3s.,Nutritional and No Fishy Aftertaste: Because our krill oil softgels stay intact well into your intestines rather than dissolving in your stomach, you can say goodbye to those fishy burps that come after ingesting a regular fish oil pill. Krill oil is also bound to phospholipids instead of triglycerides, so our krill oil supplement is easier to absorb.,Supplement for Optimal Wellness: Fight free radicals and support optimal digestion, immune system, brain, liver, joint, and heart health, and reduce swelling!,Easy and Convenient: Take 1 softgel per day, preferably with a meal. Each pill contains 100mg Phospholipids, 70mg Omega-3 Fatty Acids, 30mg EPA (eicosapentaenoic acid), 20mg DHA (docosahexaenoic acid), and 200 mcg Astaxanthin.,Welcome to the Path: With top-tier supplements like collagen powder, MCT powder, krill oil, and more, one can give their body what it needs to age gracefully.

title_name: 1MD Nutrition KrillMD - Antarctic Krill Oil Omega 3 Supplement with Astaxanthin, EPA, DHA | 2X More Effective Than Fish Oil | 60 Softgels
feature_bullets: 2x More Effective Than Fish Oil: KrillMD is made from sustainably-sourced Antarctic krill oil. This pure source of omega-3 fatty acids is clinically-studied to be more effective than fish oil, without the fishy aftertaste.*,Efficient Joint Support: Krill phospholipids bind to omega-3s to maximize efficient absorption so your joints get the support they need. Feel an easier time moving around thanks to more flexible joints, and reduced soreness. *,Powerful Antioxidant Activity: KrillMD contains astaxanthin, a powerful antioxidant that works to reduce common types of oxidative stress in the body for optimal joint, heart, and brain health.*,Long-Term Heart Health: EPA, the highly potent omega-3 in krill oil, helps maintain normal cholesterol levels. The combination with the antioxidant benefits of astaxanthin helps you support heart health now and later.*,Brain Health Support: Another powerful omega-3 fatty acid, DHA, helps support proper brain function. With regular supplementation, studies have found that krill oil helps promote memory, mood, and cognitive function.*

title_name: Oceanutra 100% Pure Antarctic Krill Oil, Organic Next Gen Omega 3 EPA/DHA, Sustainable & Traceable (1000mg Capsule, 60-Day Supply)
feature_bullets: Omega-3 Support | Made with the highly concentrated SuperbaBoost, Next Generation Krill Oil, Oceanutra Krill Oil is 100% Pure Wild-Caught Krill Oil and has very high Phospholipid levels at 56% (PL56). Even higher than Superba 2, which is 40% and some others claim to be krill oil, their levels can be as low as 5% which typically means they are blends and are predominantly fish oil. Look for 100% Pure Krill Oil and avoid the digestive issues often associated with fish oil.,PL 56 | More Phospholipids and Choline | Phospholipids make up 56% of Oceanutra Pure Krill Oil and also represent the building blocks of cell membranes in the body and therefore effectively deliver EPA and DHA to the blood, tissues and organs almost immediately. Supplementing the diet with Pure krill oil contributes to choline intake, which in turn supports cell membrane function and contributes to normal liver function, as well as normal lipid and homocysteine metabolism.,EPA DHA play many roles in the human body. They promote a healthy heart and help maintain normal triglyceride and blood pressure levels. DHA in particular can contribute to normal brain function and eye health. Since the human body cannot efficiently make EPA and DHA on its own, it is important that these fatty acids are supplied through the diet. title_name: VITALITOWN Antarctic Krill Oil 1000mg, with Omega-3s EPA & DHA, Antioxidant Astaxanthin, No Fishy Odor or Aftertaste, Support Brain, Heart, Eye Health, 60 Softgels
feature_bullets: Phospholipid-Bound Omega-3s with Astaxanthin: Our Krill Oil is cold pressed from pure Antarctic krill which is harvested in a sustainable way from the pristine waters, having far less potential for any toxins and industrial contamination. It is an ideal source of omega-3s (EPA & DHA) – essential fatty acids that our body does not produce on its own and must be consumed from diet or supplement. One serving provides 200 mg of EPA, 100 mg of DHA, 400 mg of phospholipds and 1500 mcg of astaxanthin.,High Bioavailability & No Fishy Aftertaste: Known as a fish oil alternative, krill oil boasts omega-3 fatty acids in their most natural phospholipid form, making them better absorbed by our body. Krill oil also contains powerful antioxidant astaxanthin and essential nutrient choline, these not found in fish oil. With two krill oil softgels daily, you reap more health benefits than your run-of-the-mill fish oil supplements.* No gross fishy aftertaste or burps that deters people from taking.,Brain, Heart, Eye & Joint Health Support*: Omega-3s are an integral part of cell membranes. Our body needs them to develop and function optimally in every stage of life. The consumption of EPA and DHA helps to support proper cognitive performance, maintain healthy blood lipid levels already within normal range, and promotes eye health.* The included astaxanthin in krill oil, the cause of red color, is responsible for reducing common types of oxidative stress and increasing joint mobility.*,All About Quality: Vitalitown Krill Oil is intended for both men and women free of artificial fillers, flavors, preservatives, and additives. All products are non-GMO, and contain no gluten, dairy, soy, egg, fish, tree nuts, or peanuts. Your satisfaction is our priority. We stand behind our products, no questions asked, no ifs, no ands, no buts. If there is any problem, just let us know and we'll do our best to make it right.,The Way To Vitality: Here in Vitalitown, we believe nutrition is an important part of feeling healthy, active, and energetic which defines Vitality. We have been committed to providing high-quality supplements curated for your unique needs, bridging the nutritional gap and adding a dash of vitality to your life. All our products are made in the USA and tested by third party for purity & potency to ensure that each and every bottle of Vitalitown products represents the highest standards.

title_name: Vegan Krill Supplement - DHA & EPA, Astaxanthin & Phospholipids - Premium Algae Oil, Plant Based, Sustainable, Mercury Free - Supports Heart, Brain, Eyes, Joint Health & Anti-Aging - 60 Softgels
feature_bullets: VEGAN KRILL OIL: Vrill. The next generation of powerful Omega-3. With Vrill, we go a step further than krill oil. Each plant-based serving contains at least 250 mg DHA, 125 mg EPA, 1500 mcg astaxanthin and 230 mg phospholipids. Vrill is a 100% vegan omega-3 supplement derived from algae sustainably farmed on land in the United States. Intake of two vegetarian capsules per day is sufficient.,HEALTHY FATTY ACIDS: DHA in combination with EPA supports the functioning of the heart, helps control the inflammatory response, and supports joint and immune system health. DHA supports the functioning of the eyes and contributes to the maintenance of normal brain function.*,ASTAXANTHIN AND PHOSPHOLIPIDS: Astaxanthin is an antioxidant that is anti-aging, as it helps protect your body cells against oxidative damage from air pollution and UV radiation.*,KRILL FREE & SUSTAINABLE: No unnecessary fishing. No damage to the marine ecosystem. Non-krill algal oil is pure and free of contaminants (such as PCBs, mercury and dioxins) that krill oil may contain.,A BRAND WITH A MISSION: We’re on a mission to protect and restore the oceans. Every package of Daily’s Omega-3 replaces 37 smiling sardines that would otherwise be caught commercially for the omega-3 that they get from eating algae.

feature_bullets: SUPERIOR GRADE & QUALITY, PURE ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Powered by SUPERBA2 Krill Oil, the most researched krill oil. Extracted from 100% traceable wild-caught Antarctic krill harvested with certified sustainable ECO-Harvesting technology and is virtually free of mercury & contaminants. Majority of the omega-3 in Superba 2 are bound to phospholipid, this enables to be more effectively incorporated into red blood cell membranes more quickly than fish oil supplement. Improves omega-3 index in the body by 2.5X. 12 times more effective in promoting healthy choline levels.,PHARMACEUTICAL GRADE, EXTRA STRENGTH, OMEGA-3 ENHANCED: PERFECT KRILL is a highly concentrated krill oil rich in Omega-3 fatty acids EPA and DHA, as well as Phospholipids and Choline, well protected by the naturally powerful antioxidant, Astaxanthin. The natural component of astaxanthin in krill oil helps maintain freshness and stability without the need for preservatives. It provides 1000mg per SUPERBA2 Krill Oil per serving.,SCIENTIFICALLY PROVEN HEALTH BENEFITS/BACKED BY MORE THAN 80 PATENTS WORLDWIDE: support healthy heart, liver, brain, vision, skin and joints, maintain homocysteine metabolism and support a healthy menstrual cycle for women.,SAFE AND EASY TO SWALLOW/DIGEST: Heavy Metal Tested, Non GMO, Gluten Free and Soy Free. SUSTAINABLE & TRACEABLE: Superba Krill is sustainably harvested and 100% traceable from sea to shelf. MADE IN NEW ZEALAND. PURIFIED IN USA.

feature_bullets: ✔️ Heart, Brain and Joint Health Supplement Bundle* – Looking for additional cognitive and joint health support?* This special bundle includes our Antarctic Krill Oil and Triple-Strength Omega-3 Fish Oil,✔️ High Concentration of Krill Oil Omega 3 – Viva Naturals Krill Oil delivers 1,250 mg of omega 3 krill oil, providing 165 mg of EPA and 90 mg of DHA per serving, as well as one of the highest levels of astaxanthin available among krill oil dha supplements.,✔️ No Fish Burps & Aftertaste – Our Krill Oil is virtually odorless and tasteless, without the smelly aftertaste found in low-quality krill oils. Unlike other krill oils, ours is encapsulated in innovative Caplique capsules to help prevent fishy burps.,✔️ Pharmaceutical Grade Omega 3 Supplement with Superior Absorption – Inferior fish oil supplements use ethyl ester omega-3s. Our fish oil omega 3 is delivered in triglyceride form, which is a better-absorbed form of omega 3 fatty acids.,✔️ IFOS 5-Star Certified - Our fish are wild caught using sustainable fishing practices – never farm raised. Plus, we use a combination of small fish (like sardines and mackerel), known to have less mercury and fewer toxins than bigger fish like salmon. Each batch is rigorously tested for purity and IFOS 5-Star Certified, a ranking system for premium quality fish oil.

title_name: Ultra Pure Krill Oil 500mg x 480 Capsules (4 Bottles) - Sourced in The Unpolluted Waters of Antarctic Providing a Rich Supply of Astaxanthin and Omega 3
feature_bullets: THE PUREST KRILL OIL - each capsule provides 500mg of the purest krill oil, sourced directly from unpolluted waters of the northern Antarctic. In these nutrient dense waters, the krill produce an oil that is rich in the beneficial fatty acids and nutrients.,QUALITY TESTED AND ASSURED - To offer an assurance of exceptional quality, we not only sourced the purest krill oil currently available anywhere in the world, but we spent two years finding the right manufacturing partners that held the same ideals as us. All of our supplements are made in multi-million dollar state of the art facilities across the world. Every step of the supply chain is tested and analysed along the way, and before and after product.,2X TOTAL OMEGA 3 FATTY ACIDS (230mg) - standardised to contain 23% of the beneficial Omega 3 fatty acids, including 124mg EPA and 64mg DHA per daily serving. This is 2x the concentration of most other Krill Oil supplements. WITH MARINE PHOSPHOLIPIDS, ASTAXANTHIN, VITAMIN D, AND CHOLINE - The inclusion of these important compounds in high strength ensures maximum benefit is obtained and sets krill oil apart from other fish oils.,MULTIPACK - 240 Softgels (2 bottles of 120) -8 Months supply. Compare to any other, mg for mg, bottle for bottle, this is the best value,RICH SOURCE OF ASTOXANTHIN, CHOLINE, AND PHOSPHOLIPIDS- Superba krill oil provides a richer source of astoxanthins, choline and phospholipids compared to regular krill oil. These nutrients along with the Omega 3 fatty acids give krill oil it’s beneficial properties

title_name: LYL Krill Oil Kid Gummy Bears with Vitamin D 3, Vitamin E and Vitamin A - phospholipid-Bound Omega 3 for Healthy Growth & Development - Gummy Bears with Orange, Apple & Raspberries Taste (Pack of 60)
feature_bullets: BOOST YOUR KIDS OMEGAS: If you're like most parents, you simply cannot get your kids to eat enough fruits and vegetables with omegas. Krill Oil KID EPS and DHA Gummies pack made of pure krill oil omega-3s plus daily amount of vitamin D3 and vitamins A, E, C into a tasty orange, apple & raspberries flavor gummy bear that kids love. Our win-win formula - no spoon, no mess and no fishy aftertaste.,BUILT FOR HUMAN WELLNESS: Krill Oil KID Superba Krill oil is a next generation phospholipid-complex, with omega-3s and choline straight from the pristine waters of Antarctica. Intake of OMEGA-3S fat EPA&DHA is essential for your kid’s organs to function properly, help oxygen circulation, brain development, immune support, heart health, vision, joint and skin health. Not only omega-3s, but also VITAMIN D3 that helps support healthy bone and tooth development.,CHOLINE: Choline is an essential nutrient for many body functions such as nerve signaling, liver and muscle functioning. Our body can't make enough therefore we must obtain it from our diet.,GIVE THE BEST: According to food nutrition, your kids needs such a wide range of fruits, veggies, vitamins, minerals, natural fiber, enzymes, omegas and probiotics in order to grow and be healthy, it's no wonder you can't give it everything in the course of their daily diet. LYL Krill Oil KID is is made especially as kids vitamins.,Pack of 30 delicious jelly Gummy Bears. Suggested Use: Children 2 years of age 1 gummy bear per day. ADULTS & children 12 years of age or older 2 gummies daily.

title_name: Omega Krill Oil, Food Supplement for Brain, Heart and Joint Support, Helps Manage Cholesterol Levels, Made of Pure Krill and Enriched with Omega 3, 6 and 9, 60 Softgels
feature_bullets: Pure Krill Supplement - Get your daily dose of omega 3 oil with these vitamins. Our proprietary, antioxidant-rich krill oil omega 3 contains essential, naturally-occurring fatty acids. These nutrients benefit many bodily functions and help manage cholesterol levels.,Ideal Fish Oil Alternative - Instead of a fish oil omega 3 supplement, go for our omega 3 krill oil. Our krill ingredient is sustainably sourced from the pristine Antarctic waters. So, you can enjoy the full benefits of marine nutrients without the fishy aftertaste.,Supports Heart Function - Keeping your heart in shape is a breeze with Omega Krill. Like fish oil omega 3 supplements, ours is enriched with Omega3, 6 and 9. Formulated for enhanced absorption, it works in synergy with Astaxanthin to promote optimum heart function.,Easy-to-Swallow Capsules - Omega red krill oil dietary supplements come in soft gel form, so they’re easy to take and are quickly absorbed by the body. Take 1-2 capsules with a meal daily or as advised by your wellness provider.,All-Natural Krill Oil Vitamin - These vitamin supplements are derived from crustacean shellfish. Non-GMO and lactose-free, they have no artificial colors and preservatives. (Not suitable for vegetarians and those with adverse reactions to shellfish).

title_name: Spoonful Mini Krill Oil, 375mg 130 Servings, Easy to Swallow Mini Capsults for omen and Seniors, Omega-3 DHA EPA Astaxanthin and Essential Phospholipids, Made in USA
feature_bullets: MINI KRILL OIL SOFTGELS: Our Mini Krill Oil comes in the smallest size while delivering the high potency possible. Each serving (3 capsules) contains 375mg Krill Oil with 90mg of Omega-3 Fatty Acids (50mg EPA, 24mg DHA).,4 MONTH SUPPLY: Our new mini sized Krill softgel capsules are easy to swallow and ideal for consumption by women and seniors. The suggested use is to take three (3) softgels once daily, preferably after a meal. There are 130 servings in one bottle.,ESSENTIAL NUTRITION: Krill oil is highly rich in natural antioxidant astaxanthins, omega-3 fatty acids, and EPA & DHA phospholipids. Krill oil helps support wellness, healthy joints, brain health, improve body defense systems, cognitive, cardiovascular, and heart health.,100% PURE AND SUSTAINABLE ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Our krill is harvested from the pure waters of Antarctica, safe from heavy metals, contamination, and exposure from any toxins. We source our products from a highly-regulated fishery that is regulated by the CCAMLR (Convention on the Conservation of Antarctic Marine Living Resources),MADE IN THE USA: All Spoonful products are made in the USA by a leading manufacturer in a state of the art facility complied with GMP standards. We promise to provide only the best quality products that are researched and manufactured by highly skilled researchers and engineers for our customers.
